headline: CrowdStrike vs SentinelOne: Which Cybersecurity Stock Will Outperform in 2025?
summary: Cybersecurity was a big news topic in 2024, and largely for the wrong reasons.  While there continues to be a number of high-profile security breaches, the biggest incident of 2024 was a CrowdStrike (NASDAQ: CRWD) outage that was felt around the globe.  Despite that, CrowdStrike's stock was able to recover and turned in a strong year, up about 38% as of this writing.
